title: Pixel 5 Haptics vibration rattle
content:
Hey, I have a weird resonant rattle/tick sound at the end of every haptic vibration. (I.E  incoming Notification).
It seems like it's coming from the back of the chassis speaker or mic hole (the left one). I can hear it from 30 cm away.

Updated the phone yesterday to December Pixel 5 update. 

Anybody else noticed this. Is it normal or something loose inside?

Thanks
